01:07:56.320 --> 01:08:00.452
I know you say, 'Oh, Brandon, I thought we were here to pray.'Well, we are.

01:08:00.453 --> 01:08:05.959
But I try to tell you all this because that's what I've been dealing with today.

01:08:05.960 --> 01:08:22.712
I told Diana, I said we average—if I do an average of two hours of video a day, if I do these live streams five times a week—I told her, I said, 'I do an average of 50-some hours a month of prayer videos with y'all.'50-some hours of videos because we were doing the math on it.

01:08:22.713 --> 01:08:28.231
And I said that's why a lot of you think you know me so well. I don't know you at all.

01:08:28.232 --> 01:08:31.870
When you come in public, I go—I met a guy yesterday; he goes, 'Oh, I watch you.

01:08:31.871 --> 01:08:38.350
I know you so well,'and I'm like, 'I don't know you at all.'And it's awkward for me, so I'm like, 'Okay, well, praise God.

01:08:38.351 --> 01:08:51.919
I don't know you, but you think you know me.'Okay. But after you talk to somebody—I said if I spent 50 hours a month talking to Billy Burke, I'd know him really well.

01:08:51.920 --> 01:08:57.039
And I'm just sitting here talking to a camera. But you see, I'm transparent.

01:08:57.040 --> 01:09:01.559
I don't try to hype everything up. I don't try to be something spiritually that I'm not.

01:09:01.560 --> 01:09:20.526
Y'all, I just try to go, 'Hey, we're all going to get through this and we're going to make it together.'I may be the leader right now in what God's called me to do, but I just tell you all, 'Hey, we all got issues and we all got stuff we're working through and we're all a work in progress.'And I don't care who you are.

01:09:20.528 --> 01:09:23.961
You put your clothes on the same way. You all take a poo. You all stink.

01:09:23.962 --> 01:09:28.620
You have to take a bath every single day. If you don't, you start smelling like B.O.

01:09:28.621 --> 01:09:35.399
It's just part of life. You eat, you brush your teeth, and if you don't, your breath stinks.

01:09:35.400 --> 01:09:43.919
It's just part of life. And I'm no different than you. I just told Diana, I said, 'I'm just hungry.

01:09:43.920 --> 01:09:52.439
We're just hungry.'How much do you do the fundamentals? How much do you do what it takes to be a champion?

01:09:52.440 --> 01:10:00.236
Do you want to be the Michael Jordan in faith, that you've got what it takes to be the next Michael Jordan spiritually?

01:10:00.237 --> 01:10:08.799
I'm just saying it's a metaphor. But you've got to do what nobody else is willing to do to get there.

01:10:08.800 --> 01:10:17.239
You can't act like that and just have a mentality of 'I deserve it; it's mine.'You've got to train like a champion.

01:10:17.240 --> 01:10:27.559
You've got to train like a champion spiritually. If you want what a champion has, you've got to train like a champion does.

01:10:27.560 --> 01:10:31.699
You can't act like you did in high school. You've got to come up higher.

01:10:31.700 --> 01:10:41.359
And the Lord told me, he said, 'It's not required for me to do it.

01:10:41.360 --> 01:10:53.799
You have to be as dedicated as an Olympian.'Yes. It's not just going to happen, Brandon.

01:10:53.800 --> 01:11:02.226
To come up higher requires more of you, but it's not something you deserve.

01:11:02.227 --> 01:11:06.730
Like, 'Oh, I automatically qualify for this.'It's more of Him, less of you.

01:11:06.731 --> 01:11:15.083
He said, 'The more you give of me, you get of me, and the more I have of you. If you train like a champion, you're going to be here.

01:11:15.084 --> 01:11:29.199
But if you don't, I'm not required to give it to you.'You confess your sins, all that is different than you walking like a champion.

01:11:29.200 --> 01:11:35.885
It's a bulldog mentality. He said, 'You can't be a victim. You've got to be a victor.'And that's the stuff he's rebuking me about.

01:11:35.886 --> 01:11:38.959
I'm just being real with y'all. That's what he talked to us about.

01:11:38.960 --> 01:11:44.279
If you want to walk like a winner, you've got to think like a winner.

01:11:44.280 --> 01:11:47.169
If you want to be successful, you've got to think successful.

01:11:47.170 --> 01:11:50.952
You can't sit there and think all the thoughts you've been thinking.

01:11:50.953 --> 01:11:56.979
Out of your abundant heart, your mouth speaks. You've got to change your thinking. You've got to come up higher.

01:11:56.980 --> 01:12:06.239
If you want to be successful, if you want to be where the big boys are, you've got to act like a big boy.

01:12:06.240 --> 01:12:11.926
'Oh, the devil's been messing with us. I had this going on.'Oh, no.

01:12:11.927 --> 01:12:18.736
The Lord said, 'You can't talk that way.'So I'm just telling you what he's dealing with me about.

01:12:18.737 --> 01:12:22.599
So maybe that helps you, maybe it doesn't. But there's Brandon.

01:12:22.600 --> 01:12:28.435
So, if you all want to pray with us now, you can. We love you. And we're going to jump in the river.

01:12:28.436 --> 01:12:37.566
Who wants to go tubing for a little bit? We can tube for about an hour and thirty, somewhere in there.

