01:26:35.040 --> 01:26:41.559
That's the glory of God today. I believe the glory of God is on you today.

01:26:41.560 --> 01:27:23.727
I believe it. The toe will be restored in Jesus'name. And Father, I thank you.

01:27:23.728 --> 01:27:35.919
Not only do you heal the toe, but you heal the diabetes also. We speak healing and wholeness and wellness over diabetics in Jesus'name.

01:27:35.920 --> 01:27:47.419
