01:27:47.420 --> 01:27:52.706
Father, redeem from the curse of the law that the blood sugar straightens out.

01:27:52.707 --> 01:28:02.643
I call the fire of God over that pancreas, over that digestive system in the name of Jesus and these weight issues of obesity.

01:28:02.644 --> 01:28:10.476
I speak in the name of Jesus healing and wholeness and wellness from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

01:28:10.477 --> 01:28:18.718
We call blood sugars to line up. We call restoration of the blood in Jesus'name.

01:28:18.719 --> 01:28:24.439
Nerve damage be healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

01:28:24.440 --> 01:28:33.766
Restoration of all things even in the calves and the legs. Nerve damage being healed and whole.

01:28:33.767 --> 01:28:57.679
I see healing and wholeness in the fingers in Jesus'name. I speak over the pancreas to be healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

01:28:57.680 --> 01:29:10.479
Some of you, this is a demonic spirit; you had a cultic assignment assigned to you through an elder.

01:29:10.480 --> 01:29:28.519
