01:29:28.520 --> 01:29:35.581
And the Lord Jesus Christ rebuke that devil in Jesus'name. And you're free from it from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

01:29:35.582 --> 01:29:43.519
I see it. I don't know who laid hands on you, but they shouldn't have; it was imparted.

01:29:43.520 --> 01:29:50.874
