01:30:01.400 --> 01:30:07.639
'Lay hands on no man suddenly.'Thank you, Holy Ghost. The Lord just said it.

01:30:07.640 --> 01:30:11.645
'Lay hands on no man suddenly.'That's what the scripture is.

01:30:11.646 --> 01:30:20.894
And you shouldn't let people be just touching you all the time. This was imparted by somebody. 1 Timothy 5:22.

01:30:20.895 --> 01:30:34.119
'And lay hands suddenly on no man, neither be partaker of other men's sins; keep thyself pure.'Don't be touching people quickly.

01:30:34.120 --> 01:30:39.199
Know those that labor among you. This was imparted. This is a demonic spirit.

01:30:39.200 --> 01:30:50.575
I see it, and it looked almost like a demon of black electricity.

01:30:50.576 --> 01:31:08.039
God's electricity is white, like lightning bolts, but this was a demonic electricity with yellow eyes, shaped like electricity, and it went through you like a current.

01:31:08.040 --> 01:31:23.399
This demonic spirit of diabetes was assigned to you demonically, and the Lord Jesus wants to set you free from it.

01:31:23.400 --> 01:31:33.839
That is such a strong word. I see it so clearly. I don't know who this is, but I know you're watching and the Lord is setting you free.

01:31:33.840 --> 01:31:38.052
This is a demonic spirit that has been assigned by the laying on of hands.

01:31:38.053 --> 01:31:47.959
Just as the Holy Ghost can be imparted, the devil can be imparted. Do you understand? Don't let people touch you all the time.

01:31:47.960 --> 01:31:56.048
When people say, 'I have to pray for you,'I tell them, 'Do not touch my family or me without the Holy Ghost leading you.'People say I got aggressive; I said I'd break their fingers.

01:31:56.049 --> 01:32:06.790
I meant it. I don't mean to be rude, but I'm telling you, don't touch me unless the Holy Spirit leads me to let you.

01:32:06.791 --> 01:32:19.021
Even with guest speakers at the front of the church, you see Brandon Biggs and think, 'Don't go up there,'because the Holy Spirit said, 'Don't let them touch you.'I don't let everyone touch me.

01:32:19.023 --> 01:32:28.999
I only have certain people I go to. I don't let just anyone pray for me; I let the Holy Spirit lead me.

01:32:29.000 --> 01:32:41.199
Sister Lynn was up there, and it was said, 'You can have her pray for you.'Things are imparted by the laying on of hands, both good and bad.

01:32:41.200 --> 01:32:50.359
You need wisdom concerning this, and most people do not have it. They trust too easily. You must have wisdom.

01:32:50.360 --> 01:32:55.879
Don't allow everyone to impart into you unless you feel led by the Spirit of God.

01:32:55.880 --> 01:33:15.879
I am trying to tell you from experience: do not let people touch you unless you know them or are familiar with the Holy Ghost in them.

01:33:15.880 --> 01:33:31.612
Be watchful. I am telling you this because of my own past ignorance. Be smart about this.

01:33:31.613 --> 01:33:36.651
I just saw a demonic spirit, looking like a black electric devil, that was imparted to someone.

01:33:36.652 --> 01:33:44.959
It went into you and caused diabetes, and it's trying to take your toes.

01:33:44.960 --> 01:33:50.026
Resist it. Say, 'I repent.'Father, we call it to go out in Jesus'name.

01:33:50.027 --> 01:33:55.711
We speak to you; you are free in the name of Jesus. Demonic spirit, leave them.

01:33:55.712 --> 01:34:08.359
Spirit of diabetes, be healed and whole in Jesus'name. Do not walk in fear, but be watchful and know those who labor among you.

01:34:08.360 --> 01:34:25.724
That was a very strong word. The other part concerned heart problems and heart palpitation problems.

01:34:25.725 --> 01:34:33.436
You didn't know why these palpitation problems started. You started having a heart arrhythmia.

01:34:33.437 --> 01:34:57.639
I hear the word 'heart arrhythmia'—irregular heartbeats. It is all by impartation.

01:34:57.640 --> 01:35:09.045
Some may not agree with all of it, but concerning certain individuals, this relates to the diabetic issue.

01:35:09.046 --> 01:35:17.479
I believe it is for one person, but if you receive it for yourself, say, 'I believe I am healed.'Piggyback on the word.

01:35:17.480 --> 01:35:29.879
There is an impartation you got from the demonic even concerning your heart.

01:35:29.880 --> 01:35:40.279
The heartbeats are bad; they are flutters. I see it clearly: heart flutters.

01:35:40.280 --> 01:36:02.791
You have been dealing with this for a while, but there is an expiration date on what you are going through. Today is that expiration date.

01:36:02.792 --> 01:36:23.839
The demonic spirit sent to destroy you, God is going to turn around for His glory, and you will deliver many people with the same issues.

01:36:23.840 --> 01:36:42.426
I also see spirits of depression that have been imparted. You have been walking with a cloud of darkness over your head.

01:36:42.427 --> 01:36:48.157
You feel like Eeyore from the Winnie the Pooh cartoon, thinking everything is bad.

01:36:48.158 --> 01:36:59.359
There is a darkness on your mind, but the Lord is delivering you and turning that frown upside down.

01:36:59.360 --> 01:37:03.768
The Lord says it is time for days of great joy in your household.

01:37:03.769 --> 01:37:14.381
You have been sad long enough; this assignment of depression, anxiety, and worry is over.

01:37:14.382 --> 01:37:34.439
That imparted devil is going away now in Jesus'name. He gives us a spirit of joy, peace, love, and a sound mind.

01:37:34.440 --> 01:38:57.227
You may ask where your joy has gone. The Lord also said this has to do with finances. You are imparting your tithe into bad ground.

01:38:57.228 --> 01:39:09.159
I am going to be bold and say it: you are tithing to a church that is not frugal with your money.

01:39:09.160 --> 01:39:20.177
Not all ground produces the same—some thirty, some sixty, some a hundredfold.

01:39:20.178 --> 01:39:30.039
You have had questions about where you have been giving because something didn't feel right.

01:39:30.040 --> 01:39:39.594
You felt there was corruption, but you stayed out of loyalty.

01:39:39.595 --> 01:40:15.839
You are sowing into cankerworms, and they are eating your harvest because you keep sowing into ground where they are doing bad things with your money.

01:40:15.840 --> 01:41:25.986
Look for fruit. Fruit is a representation of the root. If the fruit is bad, the root is rotten. Look at what the fruit does. Are people getting set free?

01:41:25.987 --> 01:41:42.239
Are they learning to stand on their authority as believers and fight the good fight of faith?

01:41:42.240 --> 01:41:46.056
Do you understand what I am saying? I am trying to translate what I see in the spirit into English.

01:41:46.057 --> 01:42:09.099
When I am relaying a vision, I often check if it makes sense because I am looking into the spirit realm.

01:42:09.100 --> 01:42:27.922
You communicated it well. Thanks, love. I see a tree, and I could spend all night describing every vision I have seen.

01:42:27.923 --> 01:42:39.065
The Lord said this tree would bear much fruit if you do that. I see a ministry, and the Lord sees this ministry.

01:42:39.066 --> 01:42:46.014
I see a tree and the tree goes up like this; it's big and it's green.

01:42:46.015 --> 01:42:52.413
It looks like a massive oak tree. It's a beautiful tree on the outside when you're glancing at it.

01:42:52.414 --> 01:43:00.799
But the tree is rotten with worms, termites, and infection.

01:43:00.800 --> 01:43:04.085
You can actually touch it and the tree starts to crumble inside.

01:43:04.086 --> 01:43:17.838
But then you look up inside the fruit of the tree, and there are worms and bird holes; the fruit is rotten, but the tree from a glance looks beautiful.

01:43:17.839 --> 01:43:30.034
This is a ministry that you're giving into. This is a big tree.

01:43:30.035 --> 01:43:34.232
You understand? It wasn't a little shrub; this is something big.

01:43:34.233 --> 01:43:52.679
But there's something going on in the core of it, and so it is rotten inside. So watch the fruit. Watch the fruit of where you give.

01:43:52.680 --> 01:44:14.272
You say, "Well, what's going on with my money, I guess?"I remember when the Lord said to us—we were sowing into a particular church, and the pastor was dealing with adultery.

01:44:14.273 --> 01:44:25.414
He was keeping it secret for two years. Two years messing around on his wife, and it started trickling over the congregation.

01:44:25.415 --> 01:44:32.719
The people on staff started having adulterous affairs. He was like, "Man, all these marriages are falling apart.

01:44:32.720 --> 01:44:45.330
What is going on with sister so-and-so cheating on her husband and brother so-and-so cheating on his wife?"It was spreading, and you go into the congregation and realize something's going on.

01:44:45.331 --> 01:44:57.176
Men were dealing with so much pornography and sexual perversion, and you're thinking, "Something's going on; this isn't normal."We started watching.

01:44:57.177 --> 01:45:04.973
It was hidden. I started watching, and the Lord said, "Start praying into this.

01:45:04.974 --> 01:45:08.566
I want to show you something,"because I was dealing with stuff I never dealt with before.

01:45:08.567 --> 01:45:12.169
I told her, "Something's wrong, Diana, because this is a spirit.

01:45:12.170 --> 01:45:18.690
What is this?"I started backing away from the tithe and from other things, and the Lord started teaching us stuff.

01:45:18.691 --> 01:45:26.500
I'm trying to tell you this by the Spirit of God. The Lord started giving us dreams.

01:45:26.501 --> 01:45:36.197
We started praying into it. What I'm trying to tell you is that you need to know those who labor among you. Do not trust so easily.

01:45:36.198 --> 01:45:43.559
As it was with the head of the church, it started trickling down to where you tithe and where you go to church.

01:45:43.560 --> 01:46:03.036
You say, "I never dealt with this before."I'm not blaming only the head of that church, but if you start seeing a lot of other people in that church dealing with the same thing, you start questioning yourself.

01:46:03.037 --> 01:46:10.799
Put it together; it's a picture, and the Lord is trying to warn you. Now, it's not always that way.

01:46:10.800 --> 01:46:14.606
Sometimes it's just you, and you have to deal with your flesh in other areas.

01:46:14.608 --> 01:46:22.198
It's all flesh, don't get me wrong, but I'm saying it starts trickling down onto the congregation and you can start to see it.

01:46:22.199 --> 01:46:38.599
That's what it was in this circumstance. It starts on the fruit of the tree and is distributed among the people, and you realize something is not right here.

01:46:38.600 --> 01:46:47.639
I say that's why poop rolls downhill; that's what happens. I'm just trying to be real with you.

01:46:47.640 --> 01:47:00.569
It's stuff we've learned. You start watching and realize something isn't right. Be watchful.

01:47:00.570 --> 01:47:17.079
Seeds are very important where you sow financially and who is laying hands on you.

01:47:17.080 --> 01:47:23.377
Watch those things in these last days. Do not trust so easily. Be watchful.

01:47:23.378 --> 01:47:26.785
That's why Diana and I will sow a little bit to test the ground.

01:47:26.786 --> 01:47:45.839
We watch the ground and say, "Okay, we've tested it; now be watchful over that."Then we say, "Show us, Holy Spirit, how this ground is."When you trust it, then you come and dump a lot.

01:47:45.840 --> 01:47:51.508
You say, "Listen, here is more,"and I see how you handle that.

01:47:51.509 --> 01:48:00.838
If they don't handle it right, you don't do that anymore, or you only do what the Spirit of God leads you.

01:48:00.839 --> 01:48:10.493
I believe in tithing. I believe in sowing and reaping, and I believe whatsoever a man sows, that will he also reap.

01:48:10.494 --> 01:48:24.331
I believe in thirty, sixty, and a hundredfold. I'm required to tithe by my Holy Father because I'm helping the kingdom, but I always watch how I sow my seeds.

01:48:24.332 --> 01:48:33.359
The Lord has blessed me, and He'll say, "Brandon, don't do that again."Find the good ground.

01:48:33.360 --> 01:48:40.089
Be smart with where you give. It's more important than you realize.

01:48:40.090 --> 01:48:47.039
People flippantly just do things, but it's the difference between life and death for some.

01:48:47.040 --> 01:48:49.494
You need to hear me; I'm telling you something I've learned.

01:48:49.495 --> 01:48:57.079
Do not give by emotion; give by the Spirit of the Lord. You can be led by emotion, and people will manipulate you.

01:48:57.080 --> 01:49:08.704
A good preacher praying—praise the Lord—might say, "Oh, we have a need,"while playing the keyboard, and you feel you have to sow a seed.

01:49:08.705 --> 01:49:24.130
I'm not trying to meddle, but there is spiritual, charismatic flakiness. It is always a biblical principle to give.

01:49:24.131 --> 01:49:29.912
Give, and it shall be given unto you: good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over.

01:49:29.913 --> 01:49:36.981
But know those who labor among you and where you are giving, knowing how you sow a seed.

01:49:36.982 --> 01:49:49.999
If you have a need, sow a seed. That's why we are strategic in everything we do. If we don't see fruit there, we don't do it ever again.

01:49:50.000 --> 01:50:01.025
There have been times where we have tested the ground and there has been no fruit, almost to the point where it is devoured in front of your face.

01:50:01.026 --> 01:50:15.190
We don't do that again. Be like a good farmer. A farmer knows where to plant the seed to get a good harvest.

01:50:15.191 --> 01:50:24.424
He's not going to put it in a river bottom because it will wash away.

01:50:24.425 --> 01:50:34.440
The farmer knows if he puts it in a good mix of soil, there will be a good harvest that's not full of Roundup.

01:50:34.441 --> 01:50:42.810
I'm trying to help you. I saw this by the Spirit of God because of what I saw in this tree. I didn't mean to go this way, but the Lord said I could.

01:50:42.811 --> 01:51:01.508
There are Baptists and Catholics on here—all kinds of people—and you really need to know where you're sowing.

01:51:01.509 --> 01:51:09.993
Be watchful over that. This isn't just about finances; I don't care about that.

01:51:09.994 --> 01:51:32.426
I'm telling you this to help you. There is harvester ground, warrior ground, and scholar ground.

01:51:32.427 --> 01:51:46.622
Not all ground produces the same. Watch who's a scholar and who's a harvester.

01:51:46.623 --> 01:51:52.246
When I need prayer warriors, I sow into the warrior ground. When I need a major harvest financially, I sow into harvester ground.

01:51:52.247 --> 01:51:59.232
When I sow into scholar ground is when I need wisdom. And I sow into certain ground. Brandon, you're getting way off.

01:51:59.233 --> 01:52:11.719
This is something that Dee and I pray; we pray and we sow into certain ministries based on how they are as teachers, prophets, and the anointing on their ministry.

01:52:11.720 --> 01:52:17.719
What's on their ministry? What do they impart when they're in ministry?

01:52:17.720 --> 01:52:25.119
That's what I'm trying to tell y'all. What do they do? How do they operate?

01:52:25.120 --> 01:52:31.479
Are they prayer warriors like Sister Billie? They're like barbarians, man; they'll cut the devil in half.

01:52:31.480 --> 01:52:45.479
I go to Billie Burke. Healing ground, harvester ground, amazing ground. You find ground where you have a need, and you sow a seed.

01:52:45.480 --> 01:53:06.625
So I sow and strategically give where the Lord shows me things like this, and I say, 'Listen, I'm under spiritual attack.'I go and I sow into spiritual ground like that and I say, 'Lord, I'm believing God for a harvest of this prophetic.'I need to sow into the prophetic.

01:53:06.626 --> 01:53:13.393
'Lord, I'm having problems hearing you or whatever.'So you sow into the prophetic.

01:53:13.394 --> 01:53:18.810
I sow into that, because whatever a man sows, that will he also reap. I've seen it.

01:53:18.811 --> 01:53:29.199
Healing ground, pastoral ground—it's beautiful the way the five-fold ministry is all set up.

01:53:29.200 --> 01:53:40.431
Is the mic bad? I can't hear it. No, it's okay. Like I said, let's just keep praying.

01:53:40.432 --> 01:55:03.243
I start talking too much again, but Holy Spirit, you showed us all those things so far.

01:55:03.244 --> 01:55:18.563
There has been great manipulation when it has come to finances, and people have been very wounded from this in the body of Christ, especially in the charismatic circle.

01:55:18.564 --> 01:55:36.544
God is restoring trust back. That's what He wants to say. There have been many hearts wounded because of what they would consider the prosperity gospel.

01:55:36.545 --> 01:55:41.733
God is a God of blessing, but there has been great hurt and wounds concerning prosperity preaching.

01:55:41.734 --> 01:55:53.203
There is a bad taste in a lot of people's mouths because of the way the church has handled it, and it has been abused through manipulation and unbiblical use of the platform as a blessing club.

01:55:53.204 --> 01:55:53.303
It has made people—the distaste in the world—totally leave the church because of it.

01:55:53.304 --> 01:56:48.356
There has been a lot of corruption concerning people abusing their platforms, but I'm seeing this was the enemy's plan to rob the body to the point where people don't give at all anymore.

01:56:48.357 --> 01:57:05.999
They don't help out with ministries because of this, and I don't blame them; they were hurt. There is corruption in it, and it's a perversion.

01:57:06.000 --> 01:57:15.464
But the Lord is restoring the relationship that was robbed because of mistrust of these preachers.

01:57:15.465 --> 01:57:32.518
There's great blessing in it, but it was so abused in the early 2000s and the '90s that it got off-balance.

01:57:32.519 --> 01:57:56.079
People got so upset that they left and went far right and said, 'We don't trust anything at all.'But the Lord said, 'We're now bringing restoration in the hearts of these people.'He's bringing correction to the preachers that did it.

01:57:56.080 --> 01:58:10.426
There's a purifying of the house because judgment begins in the house of the Lord.

01:58:10.427 --> 01:58:21.037
God is restoring the hurt that people have gone through. He wants your relationship and your friendship back where you trust.

01:58:21.038 --> 01:58:31.545
It wasn't the Lord that hurt you; it was just people. The love of money is the root of all evil.

01:58:31.546 --> 01:58:38.403
When you start loving money and materialism, if God can't get it through you, He won't get it to you.

01:58:38.404 --> 01:58:46.068
But you see manipulation—'if you give this certain amount, you're going to get this much'—and they lay hands on you and you fall out and all the glory.

01:58:46.069 --> 01:58:55.459
I said if I fall out, I better get up changed. In fact, when I was up there, I resisted it.

01:58:55.460 --> 01:59:01.408
Even Sister Lynn, when she was up there, she said, 'Just yield, Brandon,'because I was fighting it.

01:59:01.409 --> 01:59:08.937
I'm like, 'You're going to have to knock me on my hiney. I'm not falling until I have authentic power.'I'm just being real.

01:59:08.938 --> 01:59:20.559
I get tired of the charismatic flakiness. You're going to have to knock me on my hiney by the Holy Ghost and fire. I want real.

01:59:20.560 --> 01:59:31.104
I put my head against him like, 'Put your hand on me, and I want the Holy Ghost to lock me down with electricity.'I don't want anyone to push me down.

01:59:31.105 --> 01:59:43.786
That's why I say it, but I'm looking for it. And whenever I finally yield, I say, 'Touch me,'and boom, the power of God knocked me on my hiney.

01:59:43.787 --> 01:59:47.276
Get your flesh out of the way. That's what I'm trying to tell you all.

01:59:47.278 --> 01:59:58.639
There comes a point where you can resist it and you don't let the Holy Spirit move through you because you're so used to not wanting charismatic flakiness.

01:59:58.640 --> 02:00:16.639
You go, 'God, I just want authentic. I'm hungry for you.'There's been an abuse of it, and you just want Jesus.

02:00:16.640 --> 02:00:24.399
You want something authentic, and that's what I'm after. My job is to never lead you wrong.

02:00:24.400 --> 02:00:36.972
I never want to bring spiritual confusion or static into this prophetic movement where everyone and their brother is prophesying on YouTube, bringing confusion into the body of Christ.

02:00:36.973 --> 02:00:44.359
I'd rather not do anything at all because I told the Lord I don't want to be a voice in that.

02:00:44.360 --> 02:00:49.242
That's why I don't label myself as a prophet; I'm a watchman.

02:00:49.243 --> 02:00:56.383
If I see something and I pray it away, that's my job. I don't want to be part of the confusion.

02:00:56.384 --> 02:01:13.558
We want authenticity in these last days. So many people have been hurt by so much weirdness. Does anybody else agree?

02:01:13.559 --> 02:01:25.399
You walk away wounded and say, 'I don't care if I ever go back to church.'But you're just dealing with people, and everyone has flesh and issues.

02:01:25.400 --> 02:01:30.169
So I don't put a lot of merit in people anymore; I put it in Jesus.

02:01:30.170 --> 02:01:41.592
People will let you down—pastors, prophets, and evangelists—because we're all just human and saved by grace.

02:01:41.593 --> 02:01:49.959
But the only person who's never going to let you down is Jesus Christ, and He's here to help us win the race.

02:01:49.960 --> 02:02:03.799
I want to live long and finish strong with a good marriage and my kids raised up well, so when we get to the other side, He says, 'Well done, thou good and faithful servant.'Don't get caught up in the charismatic hype.

02:02:03.800 --> 02:02:14.479
Let's just be real, love the Lord, and pray for healings and deliverances as we operate in the giftings He told us to use.

02:02:14.480 --> 02:02:24.039
